## Scaddfolding
for automatic create vinculated laravel clases, use a command like in the the example
```bash
	php artisan scaffold create api_controller,request,model,migration Car "" "Api" ""
	php artisan scaffold delete api_controller,request,model,migration Car "" "Api" ""

	php artisan scaffold create api_controller,request,model,migration User "" "Api" ""
